# String Module - Allocation-Free String Utilities for Baremetal
#
# Provides string inspection and integer/string conversion functions
# suitable for bare-metal targets. No heap allocation.
#
# Public API:
#   - use std.string.{bm_str_len, bm_str_eq}
#   - use std.string.{bm_str_starts_with, bm_str_ends_with, bm_str_find}
#   - use std.string.{bm_int_to_str, bm_str_to_int, bm_hex_to_int}

# All functions exported from mod.spl are automatically available.
